claim.text: WebAgent significantly improves success rate on real websites by over 50% compared to baselines
claim.exact_quote: We empirically demonstrate that our modular recipe improves the success on real websites by over 50%

evidence.evidence_text: WebAgent achieves 50% higher success compared to baseline Flan-U-PaLM across real websites
evidence.limitations: Limited to three website types tested
evidence.exact_quote: WebAgent achieves best 65% success and 87.6% score on real-estate, 70% success and 85.8% score on social-media, and 80% success and 93.8% score on map, significantly outperforming single Flan-U-PaLM, or with partial language model modules (most of those achieve about 10 - 30% success)

conclusion.limitations: Limited to three specific websites, may not generalize broadly
